---
title: Home
layout: default
pagination:
  data: collections.post
  size: 10
  alias: posts
  reverse: true
---

<section id="banner">
  <div class="content">    
    <h2>Welcome to Our Workshop</h2>      
    <p>I don't Cosplay, but my daughter does and I let her use my workshop to work on her projects. I started with my father's tools, but over the decades I added more and more tools to help me with my woodworking and electronics projects. I now share my workshop with my daughter, and the posts here highlight the tools and equipment I provide her to use with her projects.</p>
    <ul class="actions">
      <li>
        <a href="/about" class="button big">Learn More</a>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>
  <span class="image object">
    <img src="/images/workshop01.jpg" alt="" />
  </span>
</section>

<h3>Posts</h3>
{% for post in posts %}
  <p>
    <a href="{{post.url}}">{{ post.data.title }}</a>, posted {{ post.date | readableDate }}<br/>
    {% excerpt post %}
  </p>
{% endfor %}

<p>
  {% if pagination.href.previous %}
    <a href=" {{ pagination.href.previous }}">Previous</a>
  {% else %}
    Previous
  {% endif %}
  /
  {% if pagination.href.next %}
    <a href=" {{ pagination.href.next }}">Next</a>
  {% else %}
    Next
  {% endif %}
</p>